{"tid":1574406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急】一人一電郵舉報","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T11:46:44.000Z","uid":264564,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a961c242a0925da3aa306a4233a884c685ed72","tid":1574406,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:44:37.000Z","msg":"（代朋友出po）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請電郵到abuse@ddos-guard.net舉報</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">電郵主題用呢個</span></span><br />\nAbuse Report and Take Down Request (Threat, Harassment, Hate Speech)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">內容copy以下整段英文字:</span></span><br />\n<br />\nHello DDOS-Guard,<br />\n<br />\nI am writing to report a web site hosted on DDOS-Guard,<br />\n<br />\nwww.hkleaks.ru<br />\n<br />\nThe web site runs against your acceptable use policy, as available at <a href=\"https://ddos-guard.net/file/aup_en.pdf,\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fddos-guard.net%2Ffile%2Faup_en.pdf%2C&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=680e7c29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ddos-guard.net/file/aup_en.pdf,</a> for at least three counts.<br />\n<br />\n● having content that is obscene, lewd, lascivious, filthy, or indecent with intent to annoy, abuse, threaten, or harass another person;<br />\n● threatening bodily harm or damage to individuals or groups;<br />\n● stalking<br />\n<br />\nThe web site is hiding behind DDOS-Guard for anonymity to reveal personal information, including direct phone numbers and residential addresses about individuals in Hong Kong, with a purpose to incite and create threat on those persons. This is also against the law of Hong Kong (Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance (Cap. 486) <a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf?FROMCAPINDEX=Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap486%21en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf%3FFROMCAPINDEX%3DY&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=b4388778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap486!en-zh-Hant-HK.pdf?FROMCAPINDEX=Y</a>)<br />\n<br />\nI strongly demand that DDOS-Guard take down the web site now, in accordance to your published acceptable use policy.<br />\n<br />\nThank you for your kind attention.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">由於不是Facebook，是直接一個網站，所以今次可能要麻煩大家copy n paste以上的，再自定標題，之後電郵到abuse@ddos-guard.net投訴</span></span>"},{"pid":"2d8ff4d91d3fc3f1634945f15d58e0e8f932f160","tid":1574406,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"88abddc11ef54e9c100c23d56cd40fe0a1006427","tid":1574406,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"6c73028c8e91c7ef14e62de1fd765e5882b727a1","tid":1574406,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"b0c6176b809a95cf6b8983eaa5418cd364d0c87f","tid":1574406,"uid":264564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a389e3a701a19d8cd6f04ed629db8c48df432dbc","tid":1574406,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.